definitions.definition: To chew with a grinding, crunching sound, and with the mouth closed.
examples: Jim was munching on a biscotti.

definitions.definition: To eat vigorously or with excitement .
examples: Watching old Bill munch his pancakes makes me hungry!

main_definition: ( often with "on" ) To chew with a grinding, crunching sound, and with the mouth closed.
secondary_definitions: To eat vigorously or with excitement .
